			<td valign="top">
				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Check that the PC pushed onto the stack is "PREV_PC+2", and that the P flags pushed onto the stack has the B bit set, but the actual P flags are not modified (B is still zero).
<br />
<br />Also, ensure the RTI instruction overwrites the B flag to zero when P is popped from the stack.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

